reviews.text:
The only reason I gave 2 star is because the staff is nice and friendly helpful. 
Otherwise I would of just given 1 star!
Sincerely don't know how the system works. 
About 20 people booked at 2pm and I was being waiting 20mins before doors are open to even register attention. I noticed people were seen before me but yet again I arrived before them ( they had 2pm appointments too) disappointed with there system,  and don't understand why people were seen before me if they arrived late and same 2pm appointments ? 
Otherwise why bother arriving early if still need to wait over hours? SOMEONE need to sort this system out!

Highly appreciated the team works for the hospital, they can always provide professional judgment for your illnesses. However, the government over-utilized the team, the A&E always over 120% usage, hope HA can solve this issue.

Racist hospital, staff can't speak English properly, huge wait times. One time I got attacked by the security staff there and ended up bleeding - all because they employ crazy staff from Dussmann security who can't speak English.
Super long wait time. Suggest all patients to go home for at least 5 hours after registration.

reviews.text: 排期極長，醫生態度惡劣，期望開放外地醫生或開發人工智能醫生，因為香港醫生實在太低質
家中長者就在這裏過身…
護士很好。紓緩治療科林姑娘,感謝您。
門診婦科，非常垃圾，新證第一次睇，只係求其比一種止血藥你，之後止痛藥要自己睇私家醫生，之後超聲波又唔照，本身已經高危，醫生自己都講啦！！乜都唔做，咁使乜睇你啫！！
😨有鬼呀😨我有個親戚個女，因為一個臨危的老人家，而被医院零晨5:OOAM急CALL去医院，佢去到時在門口走廊的一排椅坐着等進入病房，而隔離坐了一位男士，佢心想這位男士可能又係有位屋企人病重，而同自己一樣在等候，當speaker叫她可以進入病房時，一分鐘轉過身已經唔見咗個男士，當時條走廊有百幾二百米長，部升降机已lock咗，點可以咁極速跑走，之後幾日個位親戚嘅老人家仙遊了，而個位男士就是勾魂使者!
